CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 14 reads: "Glamour...Glamour...was in evidence during the tournament play and here are four examples...Center: Sisters, Iris Price Carr of Washington, D.C., standing, and Jewel Price Ross of Dallas, Tex., came as "look alikes" in dress..."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of sisters Jewel Price Ross, seated, and Iris Price Carr wearing matching outfits, posed in Fort Pitt Hotel for 24th annual American Bridge Association tournament
